title: Which Carrier for Pixel 5?
content: Hi. I'm currently with T-Mobile, but want to purchase a Pixel 5. During the purchase process, the Google site asks to "Choose your carrier". It then gives choices of "Fi Unlocked" or just "Unlocked". If I want to purchase one to try on T-Mobile, but then want to switch to Fi later, which phone should I choose?  Is there a difference between the Fi Unlocked and the Unlocked?
